<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>포인트Swap - GS THE POP</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, target-densitydpi=medium-dpi" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,address=no,email=no" />
	<meta name="description" contents=""/>
	<meta name="keywords" contents=""/>
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.ico">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
	<script src="../../js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="skipMenu"><a href="#container">본문 바로가기</a></div>
	<div class="wrapper">
		<header class="header">
			<h1>포인트Swap</h1>
			<a href="#" role="button" class="btnBack">이전 페이지 이동</a>
			<button type="button" id="qrpop" class="btnQr" title="QR코드 팝업 열기">QR코드</button>
		</header>
		<!-- //header -->
		<section id="container" class="content">
			<div class="pointSwap_Info line">
				<div class="info">
					<strong><em>전환 후</em>내 GSR리워즈</strong>
					<span>901,901P</span>
				</div>
				<div class="basicPoint">
					<strong role="text"><em class="hide">전환 전</em>내 GSR리워즈</strong>
					<span>901,901P</span>
				</div>
				<div class="btnArea">
					<button type="button" class="btnTS btnL active">선택한 제휴사 포인트 한번에 조회</button>
				</div>
			</div>
			<ul class="affiliateList line">
				<li>
					<span class="checkForm">
						<input type="checkbox" id="check01">
						<label for="check01">우리은행 위비꿀머니</label>
						<a href="#" role="text" class="versionInfo">포인트 전환 정보 확인</a>
					</span>
					<div class="con">
						<ul>
							<li class="reserve">
								<strong>보유 합계</strong>
								<span>20,999 P</span>
							</li>
							<li class="subtract">
								<strong>전환 예정</strong>
								<span class="activeInput">
									<label for="pointNum">포인트입력</label>
									<input type="number" id="pointNum"><b>P</b>
									<button type="button" class="delete">입력 내용 삭제</button>
								</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="btnArea">
                			<button type="button" class="btnTS btnL active">GSR리워즈 전환</button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span class="checkForm">
						<input type="checkbox" id="check02">
						<label for="check02">마이신한포인트</label>
						<a href="#" role="text" class="versionInfo">포인트 전환 정보 확인</a>
					</span>
					<div class="con">
						<ul>
							<li class="reserve">
								<strong>보유 합계</strong>
								<span>20,999 P</span>
							</li>
							<li class="subtract">
								<strong>전환 예정</strong>
								<span class="activeInput">
									<label for="pointNum">포인트입력</label>
									<input type="number" id="pointNum"><b>P</b>
									<button type="button" class="delete">입력 내용 삭제</button>
								</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="btnArea">
                			<button type="button" class="btnTS btnL active">GSR리워즈 전환</button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span class="checkForm">
						<input type="checkbox" id="check03">
						<label for="check03">삼성카드 보너스포인트</label>
					</span>
					<div class="con">
						<ul>
							<li class="reserve">
								<strong>보유 합계</strong>
								<span>20,999 P</span>
							</li>
							<li class="subtract disabled">
								<strong>전환 예정</strong>
								<span class="activeInput disabled">
									<label for="pointNum">포인트입력</label>
									<input type="number" id="pointNum" disabled><b>P</b>
									<button type="button" class="delete">입력 내용 삭제</button>
								</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="btnArea">
                			<button type="button" class="btnTS btnL active">취소 전환 포인트 미달</button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span class="checkForm">
						<input type="checkbox" id="check04">
						<label for="check04">BC TOP</label>
					</span>
					<a href="#" role="button" class="btnTS btnS">약관동의</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span class="checkForm">
						<input type="checkbox" id="check05">
						<label for="check05">하나은행 하나머니</label>
					</span>
					<a href="#" role="button" class="btnTS btnS">약관동의</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span class="checkForm">
						<input type="checkbox" id="check06">
						<label for="check06">NH포인트</label>
					</span>
					<a href="#" role="button" class="btnTS btnS">약관동의</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span class="checkForm">
						<input type="checkbox" id="check07">
						<label for="check07">OK캐쉬백</label>
					</span>
					<a href="#" role="button" class="btnTS btnS">약관동의</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span class="checkForm">
						<input type="checkbox" id="check08">
						<label for="check08">한전KDN빌포인트</label>
					</span>
					<a href="#" role="button" class="btnTS btnS">약관동의</a>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<dl class="notiInfo">
				<dt>이용 안내</dt>
				<dd>포인트Swap은 고객님이 보유한 다른 포인트를 GSR리워즈로 전환하는 서비스입니다.</dd>
				<dd>GSR리워즈로 전환시 취소가 불가능합니다.</dd>
				<dd>GSR리워즈로 전환하기 위한 최소 포인트는 다음과 같습니다.
					<ul>
						<li>우리은행 위비꿀머니 : 100p 이상 10p 단위</li>
						<li>마이신한포인트 : 10p 이상 1p 단위</li>
					</ul>
				</dd>
			</dl>
		</section>
		<!-- //container -->
	</div>
	<!-- //wrapper -->
</body>
</html>

